Definition: a port city on the southwestern coast of Honshu in Japan
Example: on August 6, 1945 Hiroshima was almost completely destroyed by the first atomic bomb dropped on a populated area
Synonyms: port, i, city, Honshu, p, a, on, the, southwestern, coast, of, in, Japan, August, was, almost, completely, destroyed, by, first, atomic, bomb, dropped, populated, area
Category: noun.location
